When in more teenage days it was - very, very - regular for
 to meet and - around maybe a certain point like around the Post Office or - the Post Office there of course was also a shop, a grocers shop and there was no strict closing hours, it was a case of it there was plenty, if there's a lot of us boys get in th
ere they might be open to almost midnight. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737622\charrsid12791982 
