\insrsid4547181\charrsid12791982 fun there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737622\charrsid12791982 . Just have a sort of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4547181\charrsid12791982 night\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7737622\charrsid12791982  enjoyment together. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4547181\charrsid12791982 
There was one or two houses which was very,very much sought after was houses where they could play a fiddle and the like of that you know.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7737622\charrsid12791982 
