They were, very much so. I presume even more so than they would be today. I mean, you never - you never - seem to worry if there was any - half a dozen or half score of you in the house, everybody took it in good part and - you would all have y
our cup of tea etcetera and bit of that and - if you very often maybe play certain games such as consequences and these kind of things or anything - little harmless thing like that and you could just do sitting round - round the fire.
